name: ChoiceExplorer
tagline: This is a repository for our ChoiceExplorer project.  A domain-independent interactive tool for visualizing and exploring recommendations based on any corpus of user profiles.  For example, visualizing collaborative filtering of course selections in a university, or items in a shopping cart.   It works with any collection of profiles!
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
